You can contact us via email at support@abzorbagames.com or by mail at Funstage GmbH, Wiedner Hauptstraße 94, 1050 Vienna, Austria. If you want to get in direct contact with our Data Protection Officer, including for requests, questions or concerns regarding our Privacy Policy or security vulnerabilities, please do so in writing at dpo@greentube.com.
